      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i keep getting a 500 error on our /api/v1/checkout/process endpoint whenever a user tries to apply a discount code. i've attached the partial logs below but it's super intermittent. can u see what's up?\n\n[2023-10-27 14:22:01] ERROR: Internal Server Error - RequestID: 8829-xf2\n[2023-10-27 14:22:01] STACKTRACE: Unhandled exception in DiscountService.apply(DiscountObject dto)\n[2023-10-27 14:22:01] java.lang.NullPointerException: Cannot invoke \"com.store.models.Coupon.getExpiryDate()\" because \"coupon\" is null\n[2023-10-27 14:22:02] ERROR: Internal Server Error - RequestID: 8830-xf4\n[2023-10-27 14:22:02] STACKTRACE: Unhandled exception in DiscountService.apply(DiscountObject dto)\n[2023-10-27 14:22:02] java.lang.NullPointerException: Cannot invoke \"com.store.models.Coupon.getExpiryDate()\" because \"coupon\" is null",
