      "content": "yeah i checked the code and it looks like the coupon is fetched from the DB right before that call, so it should be there. but it's just random. like, most of the time it works fine, then boom, null pointer. any idea why it would be null only occasionally? maybe some weird edge case with the database connection or something?",
